{"tid":1589941,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無考慮叫「支持白警」口號","createTime":"2019-09-23T13:22:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T13:43:43.000Z","uid":303044,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ab6872490575818c69d5c265f6496256984b265c","tid":1589941,"uid":303044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T13:22:58.000Z","msg":"我知用「支持」同「警察」連上大家都覺得有啲嘔心，但唔好俾情緒主導先。<br />\n<br />\n首先，警隊內的確係有白警既<br />\n但個大環境係黑警當道佢地本來就好辛苦<br />\n仲要俾我地屌埋一份，對佢地都唔多公道既<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/277129625984144/posts/913128755717558?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F277129625984144%2Fposts%2F913128755717558%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=%2B%2BEjZc3BRqGg7MXYxMXK6%2BaWbb7ReRbDtXxzMsl%2FlTw%3D&h=7d7e15bc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/277129625984144/posts/913128755717558?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n裡面講到<br />\n黑警呢道牆係好硬既<br />\n但如果得到白警既合作<br />\n從裡面滲透返而仲有可能贏到警察呢道牆<br />\n佢地都想獨立調查，佢地都想唔使俾黑警阿頭指示<br />\n所以大叫支持白警係無問題既<br />\n再進一步如何合作可以再計<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，就算起黑警面前大叫支持白警<br />\n佢地在公在私都唔可以視之為挑釁<br />\n無人會認自己係黑警，但黑警知道我地唔支持佢，只係唔明屌柒佢姐，同時我地俾啲白警支持。<br />\n<br />\n唔知大家點睇"},{"pid":"dc415e4e36a9e18ae4298ee4ed2da5768ea61870","tid":1589941,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T13:23:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢 (2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1589858\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1589858</a>"},{"pid":"c59744799752d71734777419259c79b597be2c2b","tid":1589941,"uid":213747,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T13:24:26.000Z","msg":"我諗天真嬌見到樓主都會甘拜下風"},{"pid":"6bc51d1cb634eab28325c1e1f7aeab1da9f59dbe","tid":1589941,"uid":7860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T13:27:30.000Z","msg":"係有白警幫手既一早幫左<br />\n老豆搵仔/放風出黎果D<br />\n唔聽指示方面 佢地一定俾上頭打壓 冇得唔聽指示<br />\n我諗冇乜用"},{"pid":"150827b8477e43ff51b44372806709a709cc6507","tid":1589941,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T13:29:26.000Z","msg":"無白警架啦 死心啦<br />\n一係低級散仔 佢支持你都冇用<br />\n為左份糧唔辭職<br />\n如果高級有白警嘅話 少少行動資訊都唔講出來？<br />\n全班仆街plan緊點洗OT錢同移民咋<br />\n透過打壓人地嘅自由 送自己去自由嘅國度<br />\n<strong>全部都係仆街來</strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">做得忍者，一定要識保護自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sjzvXH8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsjzvXH8.jpg&h=b6574070&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"be8acc1bb50eb29cf296c849483f9ebd8cf5e76a","tid":1589941,"uid":303044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"150827b8477e43ff51b44372806709a709cc6507","tid":1589941,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T13:29:26.000Z","msg":"無白警架啦 死心啦<br />\n一係低級散仔 佢支持你都冇用<br />\n為左份糧唔辭職<br />\n如果高級有白警嘅話 少少行動資訊都唔講出來？<br />\n全班仆街plan緊點洗OT錢同移民咋<br />\n透過打壓人地嘅自由 送自己去自由嘅國度<br />\n<strong>全部都係仆街來</strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">做得忍者，一定要識保護自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sjzvXH8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsjzvXH8.jpg&h=b6574070&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T13:32:54.000Z","msg":"好吧，收到"},{"pid":"e3d5216e87d8ca85e8474407f33925436ffe264b","tid":1589941,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T13:41:23.000Z","msg":"巴打都加油 我同意文宣方面可面用正面d嘅字眼拉淺黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但狗狗不鳥<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets